Comment: Correct Extraction - item was extracted correctly
Incorrect Extraction - for single item field: item was extracted incorrectly; for list item field: not applicable
Spurious Extraction - document has no information about the field, nevertheless it was extracted
Missing Extraction - document has information about the field, it was not extracted
Empty - document has no information about the field and nothing was extracted
Lists overlap: document has information about list item field, it was extracted but some items are missing and some items are spurious
